'''王辉耀'''{{BD|1958年|7月2日|catIdx=W}}，男，[[浙江|浙江]][[杭州|杭州]]人，中国经济学家，[[国务院参事|国务院参事]]，[[西南财经大学|西南财经大学]]发展研究院教授和院长，中国非政府智库[[中国与全球化智库|全球化智库]]（CCG）创始人、理事长<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/video/2018-01/31/c_129803084.htm|title=《全球智库报告2017》发布 中国智库数量居世界第二|accessdate=2018-09-23|work=新华网|archive-date=2018-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180920011112/http://www.xinhuanet.com/video/2018-01/31/c_129803084.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://repository.upenn.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1018&context=think_tanks|title=2019 Global Go To Think Tank Index Report|url-status=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220020326/https://repository.upenn.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1018&context=think_tanks|archive-date=2020-02-20|access-date=2020-05-14}}</ref>，人力资源和社会保障部中国人才研究会副会长，商务部中国国际经济合作学会副会长。<ref>{{Cite web|title=CCG Release|url=http://en.ccg.org.cn/ccg-release/|date=2018-05-09|website=Center for China and Globalization|url-status=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180509220026/http://en.ccg.org.cn/ccg-release/|archive-date=2018-05-09|access-date=2020-06-12}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite news|last=Allen-Ebrahimian|first=Bethany|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2020/01/stephen-schwarzman-china-surveillance-scholars-colleges/604675/|title=The Moral Hazard of Dealing With China: Academic institutions must grapple with the question of when engagement becomes complicity.|date=January 11, 2020|work=[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]]|access-date=2020-02-14|url-status=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200115165614/https://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2020/01/stephen-schwarzman-china-surveillance-scholars-colleges/604675/|archive-date=2020-01-15}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hudson.org/research/14330-the-curious-case-of-mr-wang-and-the-united-front|title=The Curious Case of Mr. Wang and the United Front|last=Parello-Plesner|first=Jonas|date=May 11, 2018|website=[[Hudson_Institute|Hudson Institute]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180521144201/https://www.hudson.org/research/14330-the-curious-case-of-mr-wang-and-the-united-front|archive-date=2018-05-21|access-date=2019-07-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2018/05/07/rubio-questions-d-c-panel-on-china-influence-united-front-beijing-communist-party/|title=Rubio Questions D.C. Panel on China Influence|last=Allen-Ebrahimian|first=Bethany|date=May 7, 2018|website=[[Foreign_Policy|Foreign Policy]]|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508054738/https://foreignpolicy.com/2018/05/07/rubio-questions-d-c-panel-on-china-influence-united-front-beijing-communist-party/|archive-date=2018-05-08|access-date=2019-07-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>

广东外语外贸大学77级本科毕业，在北京国家经贸部工作，后在加拿大[[溫莎大學|温莎大学]]、[[西安大略大学|西安大略大学]]和英国[[曼彻斯特大学|曼彻斯特大学]]留学，获工商管理硕士学位（MBA）和国际管理博士学位（PhD）。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Cheng|first=Li|title=The Power Of Ideas: The Rising Influence Of Thinkers And Think Tanks In China|publisher=World Scientific|year=2017|isbn=978-981-310-025-1|language=en}}</ref>

曾经担任[[肯尼迪政府学院|哈佛大学肯尼迪政府学院]]高级研究员，<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ash.harvard.edu/people/huiyao-wang|title=Huiyao Wang|website=ash.harvard.edu|language=en|access-date=2019-10-09|archive-date=2019-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009134614/https://ash.harvard.edu/people/huiyao-wang|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[布鲁金斯学会|布鲁金斯学会]]客座研究员，<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.de/books?id=ofmtDgAAQBAJ&pg=PA38&lpg=PA38&dq=%22harvard%22+%22wang+huiyao%22+%22senior+fellow%22&source=bl&ots=76GoezpGxg&sig=ACfU3U0ouothVhpzUjsM_-KbdgUbDcw4ow&hl=zh-CN&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiKiq7ahY3lAhWR_aQKHfRaB_Q4ChDoATAAegQICRAB#v=onepage&q=%22harvard%22%20%22wang%20huiyao%22%20%22senior%20fellow%22&f=false|title=Power Of Ideas, The: The Rising Influence Of Thinkers And Think Tanks In China|last=Cheng|first=Li|date=2017-03-14|publisher=World Scientific|isbn=9789813100251|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Cheng|first=Li|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ofmtDgAAQBAJ&q=wang+huiyao+University+of+Manchester&pg=PA37|title=Power Of Ideas, The: The Rising Influence Of Thinkers And Think Tanks In China|date=2017-03-14|publisher=World Scientific|isbn=978-981-310-025-1|language=en|access-date=2021-06-08|archive-date=2021-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617064302/https://books.google.com/books?id=ofmtDgAAQBAJ&q=wang+huiyao+University+of+Manchester&pg=PA37|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[北京大学|北京大学]]、[[清华大学|清华大学]]、[[中国政法大学|中国政法大学]]，加拿大[[西安大略大学|西安大略大学]]等多家大学兼职教授。

